des:
This skill provides a random snarky, motivational or fun pop culture quote daily. Add a layer of spontaneity to your day. Listen to a curated set of funny, uplifting and sometimes snarky quotes designed to make you laugh, encourage, and think. The skill is a product of MyGoodQuotes. MyGoodQuotes is a service that allows you to save and share your favorite quotes from family and friends. To learn more, visit us at https://mygoodquotes.com.

Have feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Just email admin@mygoodquotes.com with the subject line: MyGoodQuotes skill
